title: The Prophecy Club. Ken Peters - I Saw the Tribulation
description: Ken Peters, a prophet of God, gives about 10,000 personal prophecies a year with extreme accuracy, and with signs following. Ken has just been released to tell two dreams given to him over 20 years ago. He also explains some events that have already come to pass and powerful sequential detailed endtime world events--from judgment on the nations, to revival and unprecendented persecution. Ken gives clear direction for future preparation of God&#039;s people.
